      <title>乌干达反对党领袖贝西杰的妻子称其在肯尼亚“被绑架”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/uganda-opposition-leader-besigye-kidnapped-in-kenya-wife-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据乌干达反对派领导人基扎·贝西杰 (Kizza Besigye) 的妻子称，他上周末在邻国肯尼亚首都被拘留，并被转移到坎帕拉，目前被关押在军事监狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/uganda-opposition-leader-besigye-kidnapped-in-kenya-wife-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 08:53:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桥水基金称特朗普可能会选择更为包容的美联储主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/bridgewater-says-trump-may-pick-more-accommodating-fed-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桥水基金联席首席投资官鲍勃·普林斯周三表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税、财政刺激和移民政策可能会导致美国无法实现 2% 的通胀目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/bridgewater-says-trump-may-pick-more-accommodating-fed-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 08:13:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石破茂承诺进行税收谈判，刺激计划获批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/japan-s-stimulus-package-gets-dpp-nod-with-tax-talk-inclusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本国民民主党高级官员滨口诚称，日本首相石破茂与主要反对党就经济刺激方案达成协议，承诺将把讨论反对党的减税提案纳入其中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/japan-s-stimulus-package-gets-dpp-nod-with-tax-talk-inclusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 06:54:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税计划或将对泰国经济造成 46 亿美元冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/thai-economy-seen-taking-4-6-billion-hit-from-trump-tariff-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项研究表明，如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普履行承诺提高美国进口商品关税，泰国明年可能无法实现其增长目标，因为这可能会损害这个东南亚国家的出口并削弱其货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/thai-economy-seen-taking-4-6-billion-hit-from-trump-tariff-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 06:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
