      <title>人权观察称沙特财富基金是压制批评者的工具</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/saudi-arabia-wealth-fund-pif-a-tool-to-silence-critics-human-rights-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人权观察组织在一份报告中指出，沙特阿拉伯王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼担任主席的主权财富基金已成为该国压制国际批评的重要工具。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/saudi-arabia-wealth-fund-pif-a-tool-to-silence-critics-human-rights-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 05:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
