    <item>
      <title>里约混乱表明特朗普回归前世界就已经失去控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/chaos-in-rio-shows-a-world-untethered-even-before-trump-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯匹林纳鸡尾酒在流淌，桑巴舞和弗雷沃舞者在摇摆，轻柔的海风笼罩着里约热内卢的贵宾。但随着二十国集团公报在网上出现，气氛却远非喜庆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/chaos-in-rio-shows-a-world-untethered-even-before-trump-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其希望特朗普解决 S-400 争端并购买 F-35</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/turkey-pins-hopes-on-trump-to-resolve-s-400-feud-and-buy-f-35s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在等待总统乔·拜登采取行动多年后，土耳其将希望寄托在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普身上，希望他能解除因使用俄罗斯防空系统而受到的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/turkey-pins-hopes-on-trump-to-resolve-s-400-feud-and-buy-f-35s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 19:34:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
